snippet.title: Gas Station Simulator Demo Video
snippet.description:
Check out Gas Station Simulator on Steam and add it to your wishlist: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1149620/Gas_Station_Simulator/

We created a demo of Gas Station Simulator for the Steam Game Festival (7h to 13th October) and here is a teaser video of what you can expect and how the game looks right now.
